    "text": "(Comedy)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 147.69,
    "endTime": 148.733,
    "text": "(Feel Good, Netflix Original) You want to kiss me, mate?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 148.733,
    "endTime": 149.983,
    "text": "That would be so cool."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 150.652,
    "endTime": 151.23399999999998,
    "text": "Now?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 151.235,
    "endTime": 151.70000000000002,
    "text": "Yes."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 151.7,
    "endTime": 155.28099999999998,
    "text": "Your father and I want to know if you found a new narcotics anonymous meeting."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 155.282,
    "endTime": 156.282,
    "text": "A what meeting?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 156.783,
    "endTime": 157.908,
    "text": "I'm Mae, I'm an addict."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 157.91,
    "endTime": 159.743,
    "text": "On My Block: Season 3, Netflix Original Do y'all still need me?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 159.743,
    "endTime": 160.453,
    "text": "- Yes. - No."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 160.453,
    "endTime": 164.165,
    "text": "Jasmine, the reason we're acting so cagey is because this situation is life or death."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 165.708,
    "endTime": 167.168,
    "text": "Please, take a drink, hydrate."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 167.168,
    "endTime": 168.46200000000002,
    "text": "Let me know if it's too strong."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 168.462,
    "endTime": 169.378,
    "text": "Is what too strong?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 169.378,
    "endTime": 170.422,
    "text": "The poison."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 171.338,
    "endTime": 172.84,
    "text": "(Marc Maron: End Times Fun, Netflix Original) I'm not judging your faith."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 172.84,
    "endTime": 174.508,
    "text": "Do whatever you gotta do to get by, right?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 174.508,
    "endTime": 176.845,
    "text": "Jesus, Buddha, Allah, Yahweh."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 176.845,
    "endTime": 179.847,
    "text": "The Marvel Universe, I think, works for some people."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 179.847,
    "endTime": 181.598,
    "text": "It's a very popular belief system."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 181.683,
    "endTime": 184.435,
    "text": "(Taylor Tomlinson: Quarter-Life Crisis, Netflix Original) All my friends are like, \"You need a guy with a car and a job.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 184.435,
    "endTime": 187.438,
    "text": "And I'm like, \"Yeah, but then I have to deal with his wife, like it's a whole thing.\""
